coincident              Determine coincident coordinates
cov.sp                  Calculates spatial covariance
cov.st                  Calculates spatio-temporal covariance
decomp.cov              Calculates decomposition of covariance matrix
dist1                   Calculate Euclidean distance matrix for a
                        matrix of coordinates
dist2                   Calculate Euclidean distance matrix between
                        coordinates of two matrices
get.contours            Extracts coordinates from contourLines function
krige.ok                Performs Ordinary Kriging
krige.sk                Performs Simple Kriging
krige.uk                Performs universal kriging
maxlik.cov.sp           Determines maximum likelihood estimates of
                        covariance parameters
maxlik.cov.st           Determines maximum likelihood estimates of
                        covariance parameters
mspe.uk                 Calculates mean-square prediction error of
                        Universal Kriging predictions
plot.contourLines       Plot contour lines
pweights.uk             Calculates Universal Kriging weights
rcondnorm               Generate from conditional normal distribution
rmvnorm                 Generates realizations from a multivariate
                        normal distribution
simple.cov.sp           Calculates spatial covariance based on distance
                        matrix
simple.cov.time         Calculates temporal covariance based on
                        distance matrix
spLMPredictJoint        Returns posterior predictive sample from spLM
                        object
toydata                 A toy data set for use in examples.
